ATTRIBUTION
================================================================================

GaussMatrix is a derivative work built on the Tuwunel codebase. GaussMatrix
adopts Tuwunel's architecture, protocol behaviour, and on-disk compatibility as
its specification and extends it toward a sovereign, horizontally-scalable,
agentic-AI-ready Matrix homeserver.

  Tuwunel — High Performance Matrix Homeserver in Rust
  https://github.com/matrix-construct/tuwunel
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Tuwunel is itself the successor to conduwuit and Conduit. GaussMatrix gratefully
acknowledges the contributors of the entire lineage:

  - Tuwunel Contributors
  - conduwuit Contributors      (https://github.com/girlbossceo/conduwuit)
  - Conduit Contributors        (https://gitlab.com/famedly/conduit)
  - Timo Kösters
  - June Clementine Strawberry
  - Jason Volk

